{"tid":665010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網劇獻首個床戲 鄭欣宜：冇諗過要露的都露了","createTime":"2018-05-14T14:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T15:45:27.000Z","uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"46ac3c0a5e6faecba6d2818e6f288bba1907b333","tid":665010,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:36:29.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】鄭欣宜和何佩瑜（Jeana）、陳綺雯（Aki）、雨僑、連詩雅和陳嘉莉拍攝網劇《性敢中環》外景戲，雖然只是一個聚會場口，但6個女仔分別作斜膊、露肩、露腿打扮，疑似搶先開戰！<br />\n<br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\">　欣宜透露劇中獻出人生的首個牀戲，與鄧健泓有牀上激戰，相當刺激，拍攝期間更被扯掉被子，連沒想過要露的部份也露了</span>；欣宜還抵死自言較適合做動作演員，事關演文戲會NG，但這些動作戲就1、2個take完成。<br />\n<br />\nAgeiess美國原裝進口第二代救急眼霜，60秒極速收緊眼袋！瞬間去除皺紋，消除浮腫！<br />\n<br />\n　　相反Jeana以身體有雀斑為由、收起性感；搞笑是當欣宜提到Jeana劇中最多對手戲的人是栢天男，即興奮高呼對方是一個大靚仔，還曾經跟對方拍MV並附有親吻鏡頭，只是最後怕尷尬而刪剪了；隨即被取笑「識食」及鍾情「國際菜」。<br />\n<br />\n　　Aki在劇中飾演愛夜蒲，遇上心儀的男神或高質素的男人，更敢於主動出擊，估計少不免會有短裙、tube-top等戰衣，但她自言有激動無激情，尚未獻出螢幕初吻的她亦不介意有大膽鏡頭，並已設下不能露點的底線。 Aki稱由於單身，可自己話事不用問准另一半，不過昨日母親節就被阿媽催婚，指她不再是「十八廿二」、小心變老姑婆；Aki稱寧缺勿濫，因希望拍拖的對象就是真命天子，所以急不來，但卻強調：「性感和夜蒲都是劇情需要，好男人唔好驚到唔敢埋身呀。」"},{"pid":"6025d8878f0806dedaa3d422c8c2900dcddff1ef","tid":665010,"uid":137096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"講還講...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ee684431df2530d1a4fcddd9b6235e6dc38d6f","tid":665010,"uid":96,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T14:57:42.000Z","msg":"係咪個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36dcbc735365b1d41e263a3f79896886cc47aebc","tid":665010,"uid":41292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:06:31.000Z","msg":"鄧健泓RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好鐘意聽你首呀四架"},{"pid":"7b4dafdc78e560810185561976303a28b5c195f9","tid":665010,"uid":36029,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:24:53.000Z","msg":"見到床戲、露，第一時間就想㩒入黎睇<br />\n點知㩒落去嗰剎那，先見到鄭欣宜呢三個字<br />\n心諗，仆街了，返唔到轉頭了<br />\n入到黎希望冇圖，點知原來真係純文字討論<br />\n好彩，好彩"},{"pid":"c76e4044281a22234bf9b25abb6c102337ca0a06","tid":665010,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"b5a658f616afe485e6ca661696635961b1e4d790","tid":665010,"uid":45232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"好彩無圖"},{"pid":"2d0e0bdc33c47c191789972454d483f74b645a51","tid":665010,"uid":14910,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b60a23e915fd5cc753325c4adab158afac321fa9","tid":665010,"uid":76181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d0e0bdc33c47c191789972454d483f74b645a51","tid":665010,"uid":14910,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/princejoyce\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fprincejoyce&d=ZB1ESaTuGoET0BYUrCG2VRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d2c4cc3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/princejoyce</a><br />\n自己上去睇飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5990afbe31ae343bdfe095ff1d8f17270c70bb29","tid":665010,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:35:54.000Z","msg":"旗已扯"},{"pid":"7bb49e423571d0753b23e4d2ec3d5c6d53a2ce84","tid":665010,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d0e0bdc33c47c191789972454d483f74b645a51","tid":665010,"uid":14910,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T15:39:27.000Z","msg":"自動自覺開ig睇啦"},{"pid":"7ef44843d1015e13458e53155618f69ac15d0ffe","tid":665010,"uid":62011,"like":0,"d